NAME

	Data::Util - A selection of type-related utilities

SYNOPSIS

	use Data::Util qw(:all);

	use Data::Util -fast_isa;

DESCRIPTION

	This module provides utility subroutines related to data types.

	See "perldoc Data::Util" for the rest of the document.

DEPENDENCIES

	perl 5.8.1 or later, and a C compiler.

INSTALLATION

	To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

